{
  "stem": "24409.10",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I gave some of the languages which I spoke.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was drafted and was sent to the induction center at-- I don't remember the name.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was the [INAUDIBLE] Induction Center in New Jersey.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there I was, from there I was sent within three weeks, assigned through the, through the, through the quartermaster training center in Fort Lee, Virginia.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I've never been through, through the basic, basic training.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As soon as I arrived, I [? told, ?] I had trouble, first of all, with the sergeant.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I, I'm a very un-handy person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I was supposed to make the bunk, I had trouble with it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, I went to the sergeant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the sergeant was a typical southerner, professional sergeant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The sergeant was actually a corporal and from the south.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Very nice, very tough, and very stupid, I think, but very nice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I told him, listen, I want to know, Corporal, whether in the Army your, your, your superior of you, is he only for the training, or whether he can come to you with your-- with his personal problems, too?",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, sure, son.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you have a personal problem, this is our problem.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Your problem is my problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What is your problem?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I told him, you will find me good when it comes to repeat the instruction with to learn the general orders that you have to learn by heart-- general orders.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I have suffered all my life by my un-handiness.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so he says, oh, let's [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, when we get these sticks-- we didn't have rifles to train with.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were not enough rifles here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I always lose the, lose the stick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I can't make the bunk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I try, but it never comes out.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
